          1701 DOMMRG Combines design model datablocks for MultiOPT Main Index MultiOPT is a toolkit application that allows the user to combine up to five optimization tasks. The DOMMRG module combines the datablocks from the individual models to create a merged version that can be used in the DOM9 optimization module.
